T16TD4404E:341a-0: @341a # // bcom ldan @341b 'das la lha'i dbang po rab dga' ldan gyis bkra shis kyi tshigs su bcad pa //
T16TD4404E:341a-1: dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal lo //
T16TD4404E:341a-2: bkra shis dam pa gang zhig gis //
T16TD4404E:341a-3: chags pa med pa'i zla bar mtshan gsol mtshan btags pa //
T16TD4404E:341a-4: pho brang mchog tu rab gshegs pa //
T16TD4404E:341a-5: des ni 'dir yang bkra shis legs gyur cig / bkra shis dam pa gang zhig gis //
T16TD4404E:341a-6: ye shes mtha' yas dbang zhes bya bar mtshan btags pa //
T16TD4404E:341a-7: kha dog gser du rab gshegs pa //
T16TD4404E:341a-8: des ni 'di yang bkra shis legs gyur cig / bkra shis dam pa gang zhig gis //
T16TD4404E:341a-9: kun du mtha' yas spyan zhes bya bar mtshan btags pa //
T16TD4404E:341a-10: padmo'i rtse mor rab gshegs pa //
T16TD4404E:341a-11: des ni 'dir yang bkra shis legs gyur cig / bkra shis dam pa gang zhig gis //
T16TD4404E:341a-12: yan lag rin po che zhes bya bar mtshan btags pa //
T16TD4404E:341a-13: rin chen mdzod du rab gshegs pa //
T16TD4404E:341a-14: des ni 'dir yang bkra shis legs gyur cig /
T16TD4404E:341a-15: bkra shis dam pa gang zhig gis //
T16TD4404E:341a-16: dpal rab rgol ba'i stag ces bya bar mtshan btags pa //
T16TD4404E:341a-17: dbang po'i khang par rab gshegs pa //
T16TD4404E:341a-18: des ni 'dir yang bkra shis legs gyur cig / bkra shis dam pa gang zhig gis //
T16TD4404E:341a-19: yon tan thams cad ston pa'i nyi mar mtshan btags pa //
T16TD4404E:341a-20: me tog snying por rab gshegs pa //
T16TD4404E:341a-21: des ni 'dir yang bkra shis legs gyur cig / bkra shis dam pa gang zhig gis //
T16TD4404E:341a-22: yan lag 'od zer mtha' yas par ni mtshan btags pa //
T16TD4404E:341a-23: shing gis brgyan par rab gshegs pa //
T16TD4404E:341a-24: des ni 'dir yang bkra shis legs gyur cig / bkra shis dam pa gang zhig gis //
T16TD4404E:341a-25: mgon po the tshom 'joms pa chos kyi rgyal mtshan de //
T16TD4404E:341a-26: rin chen khang par rab gshegs pa //
T16TD4404E:341a-27: des ni 'dir yang bkra shis legs gyur cig / bkra shis dam pa gang zhig gis //
T16TD4404E:341a-28: mi yi seng ge ye shes sgron ma mtha' yas pa //
T16TD4404E:341a-29: spos kyi rtse mor rab gshegs pa //
T16TD4404E:341a-30: des ni 'dir yang bkra shis legs gyur cig / bkra shis dam pa gang zhig gis //
T16TD4404E:341a-31: sangs rgyas yon tan kun gyi 'byung gnas 'od mnga' ba //
T16TD4404E:341a-32: nor bus brgyan par rab gshegs pa //
T16TD4404E:342a-0: des ni 'dir yang bkra shis legs gyur cig / ces pa ni bcom ldan 'das la lha'i rgyal po rab dga' ldan @342a * //
T16TD4404E:342a-1: gyis bkra shis kyi tshigs su bcad pas bstod pa'o //
T16TD4404E:342a-2: sangs rgyas phal po che las gsungs pa'i bkra shis kyi tshigs su bcad pa'o /
